<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.centreon.com/">
Centreon</weblink>: PHP/MySQL frontend for Nagios, add some functionnalities and simplify configuration</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.nagvis.org/">
NagVis</weblink>: Addon for the visualization of the monitoring results</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

