 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://vanheusden.com/check_nagios_summary/">
check_nagios_summary</weblink>: check_nagios_summary enables you to do perform distributed monitoring using Nagios</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.vanheusden.com/nagircbot/">
